document_data.name: Nalander
document_data.mainbody: '''Nalander''' was a noble family of [[Cormyr]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.History: In the {{YearlinkName|1479}}, Lord Arkanon Nalander schemed to place someone on the [[Dragon Throne]] other than a member of the [[Obarskyr]] family. He was backed by persons in [[Sembia]]. His fellow schemers included Lord [[Elbert Oldbridle]].
document_data.Members:
* Lord [[Arkanon Nalander]], head of the family ''circa'' 1479 DR.
* [[Arkeld Nalander]], his son.
